column6: "DEAD STARS" The first arc reaches its conclusion! Mer-z-bow will never be the same! Upheaval imminent! Bucky Barnes, the Winter Soldier -- face to face with Crossbones! The mystery figure who took a shot at Bucky learns the cost of his transfiguration. Daisy Johnson causes an earthquake. Ventolin acts.
column8: | penciller (cover):Mike Del Mundo | writer:Ales Kot | artist:Marco Rudy
